title: AOC -LIVE on Election Day - NYC Go Vote Today!
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Congresswoman Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez joins Rosenberg and Laura Stylez LIVE on-air to talk about today's June 22nd election. AOC gives her endorsements and talks about police funding!
